{"word":"G2350 - θορυβέω - thorybéō - thor-oo-beh'-o - Make ado","slug":"G2350","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θορυβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>thorybéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>thor-oo-beh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make ado"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03C5;&#x03B2;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - thorubeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>thor-oo-beh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2351\">G2351</a>; to <i>be in tumult</i>, that is, <i>disturb</i>, <i>clamor:</i> - make ado (a noise), trouble self, set on an uproar."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2351\">G2351</a>, <a href=\"#/G5182\">G5182</a>"}]}